text.tspan: Share of SARS-CoV-2 sequences that are the delta variant
Shown is the delta variant's share of total analyzed sequences in the preceding two weeks.
Data source: GISAID, via CoVariants.org – Last updated 17 July 2024
Note: This share may not reflect the complete breakdown of cases, since only a fraction of all cases are sequenced.
Recently-discovered or actively-monitored variants may be overrepresented, as suspected cases of these variants are likely to be
sequenced preferentially or faster than other cases.
